281
00:22:35,024 --> 00:22:35,854
Tu n'es pas morte.

282
00:22:36,304 --> 00:22:37,453
Vous non plus.

283
00:22:38,504 --> 00:22:39,459
Mais...

284
00:22:41,304 --> 00:22:42,020
Peu importe.

285
